  "blurb": "A magnificent beachfront villa set across five levels on a sandy cove just north of Chaweng, with two swimming pools — an 18-metre and a 12-metre — an oversized jacuzzi and direct sand below. Seven bedrooms plus two children’s dorms, a gym and spa sala, fully staffed with a private chef. From $1,530 a night.",
  "detail": "Built right onto the beach on a quiet sandy cove a little north of Chaweng, this seven-bedroom villa unfolds over five levels, every room turned toward the sea and the islands beyond. It is designed for big groups who want to settle in and want for nothing.\n\nOutdoor living is the centrepiece: two swimming pools — an eighteen-metre and a twelve-metre — an oversized jacuzzi, sun decks and a beachfront sala step down to the powder-soft sand. Open-plan living opens fully to the deck, with a dining room beside a full kitchen and an outdoor BBQ terrace.\n\nThe seven en-suite bedrooms are arranged across the floors — king rooms with sea views, indoor and outdoor showers, the largest with an outdoor bathtub and a wide balcony — alongside two children’s dorms with twin beds, a stylish base for younger guests.\n\nEntertainment and wellness are built in, with a fully-equipped gym, a massage sala for in-villa treatments, a bar and games space. The villa is fully staffed with a manager, private chef, housekeepers, gardeners, a pool attendant and security, and a daily breakfast, a welcome lunch or dinner with wine, spa vouchers, a farewell beachfront movie night and airport transfers are all included. Offered from $1,530 a night.",
